<p><strong>查看用户配置信息：</strong></p><ul><li>进入mysql</li><li>use mysql;</li><li>select user,host,password from user;</li><li><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></li></ul><p><span style="background-color: yellow;">方法一：</span>允许所有ip地址访问 update user set host = '%' where user = 'root'</p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;">方法二：</span>grant all privileges on *.* to 'root'@'%' identified by '123456' with grant option;</p><p>配置： sudo vim /etc/mysql/my.conf</p><p>将&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(184, 204, 228);">bind-address&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;= 127.0.0.1</span>注释掉</p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>远程客户端登录：</strong></p><p>mysql -u root -p123456 -h xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx&nbsp;-P 3306</p>
